sentence: In Kota Kinabalu, United Pasokmomogun Kadazandusun Murut Organisation (UPKO) led by its Secretary-General Datuk Wilfred Madius Tangau, on 23 September 2008, joined its 3 other Barisan Nasional (BN) counterparts Malaysian Chinese Association, Parti Gerakan Rakyat Malaysia and Malaysian Indian Congress, petitioning Government review of ISA.
